
🧑‍🎓 Student Zone

| Page                     | Purpose                             |
| ------------------------ | ----------------------------------- |
| `/student/profile/`      | View and update profile             |
| `/student/enrollments/`  | View enrolled courses               |
| `/student/marks/`        | Marks & grades                      |
| `/student/cultural/`     | View & register for cultural events | 
| `/student/projects/`     | View & submit lab/project work      |
| `/student/achievements/` | Showcase certificates & recognition |
| `/student/dashboard/`    | Overview of academics + activities  |

👩‍🏫 Teacher Zone

| Page                             | Purpose                                 |
| -------------------------------- | --------------------------------------- |
| `/teacher/courses/`              | Courses handled                         |
| `/teacher/students/<course_id>/` | Students in a course                    |
| `/teacher/marks/upload/`         | Add marks for students                  |
| `/teacher/projects/manage/`      | View + evaluate lab/project submissions |
| `/teacher/events/evaluate/`      | Judge events or view participation      |
| `/teacher/profile/`              | View/update personal info               |

🧑‍💼 Admin Zone

| Page                      | Purpose                                    |
| ------------------------- | ------------------------------------------ |
| `/admin/dashboard/`       | Full system overview                       |
| `/admin/degrees/add/`     | Add degrees                                |
| `/admin/departments/add/` | Add departments                            |
| `/admin/courses/add/`     | Add courses                                |
| `/admin/users/manage/`    | Manage students & teachers                 |
| `/admin/events/create/`   | Create cultural events (fests, debates)    |
| `/admin/projects/create/` | Create project slots per course            |
| `/admin/reports/`         | View analytics (pass %, top scorers, etc.) |
